# Super Admin Panel вЂ” Walkthrough & Documentation

We have implemented a production-ready **Super Admin Panel** for the Study Library ERP. The panel is completely separate from the Library Owner Dashboard and is restricted exclusively to users with `role="super_admin"`.

---

