## рџ› пёЏ Tech Stack & Architecture

| Layer | Technology | Usage |
| font | Inter / JetBrains Mono | Modern SaaS Typography |
| Frontend | React + Vite + TypeScript | Strict TS types, React Router v7 |
| UI | Tailwind CSS (v4) + shadcn/ui style | Modern dark/light SaaS theme with Amber/Orange accent |
| Validation | Zod + React Hook Form | Full client-side & server-side schema validation |
| State/API | @tanstack/react-query + Axios | Caching, refetching, JWT bearer tokens & auto-refresh |
| Backend | Node.js + Express.js | Service & Controller layers, Express Async Errors |
| Database | MongoDB + Mongoose | Schema definitions, Mongo session transactions, compound indexes |
| Security | JWT + bcrypt | Role middleware (`authorize('super_admin')`), rate limiting |

